// +------------------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------+--------+
// |              subAccountId 184 (already shifted by 72bits)              |       orderId 64       | type 8 |
// +----------------------------------+----------+---------+-----------+----+--------+---------------+--------+
// |             amount 96            | profit 8 | flags 8 | unused 48 |   time 32   |      enumIndex 64      |
// +----------------------------------+----------+---------+-----------+-------------+------------------------+
// |                                                unused 256                                                |
